(37, 'Body Armour Weapon of Mass Gaining', '<div id=\"tab-product-overview-description\" class=\"woocommerce-Tabs-panel woocommerce-Tabs-panel--product-overview-description panel entry-content wc-tab\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"tab-title-product-overview-description\">\r\n<h2 class=\"yikes-custom-woo-tab-title yikes-custom-woo-tab-title-product-overview-description\">Product Overview/Description</h2>\r\n<p>Gaining muscle mass can be very challenging for people with fast metabolism when they find it difficult to consume enough calories and protein during the day. Body Armour Weapon of Mass Gaining is a high-quality mass gainer that is packed with the best quality protein, BCAA, calories and other nutrients to help you gain mass and size. Body Armour Weapon of Mass Gaining has great taste and amazing mixability.</p>\r\n<p>Addition of Ashwagandha helps in improving the testosterone level which aids in faster muscle growth, improved concentration and boosts brain function.</p>\r\n<p>Body Armour Weapon of Mass Gaining gives a powerful mix of Protein , Carbohydrates, Creatine and L-Glutamine with balanced blend of vitamins and minerals to increase power and size.</p>\r\n</div>', 'Body Armour Weapon of Mass Gaining.webp', '<p><span class=\"posted_in\"><strong>Product Highlights : </strong></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>High Quality Protein with High Quality Carbohydrates</li>\r\n<li>Designed to digest and release at varied intervals throughout the day to ensure your muscles are kept fed</li>\r\n<li>DigyZyme&reg; aids protein &amp; carbohydrate breakdown making it best mass gainer</li>\r\n<li>Helps Muscle Growth and body fuel recovery</li>\r\n</ul>', 2),
