low-fat milk.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\">It has 50 Grams of protein from a mixture of faster and slower digesting resources including Whey, casein, and Egg.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\">ON serious Mass helps to supply 250-plus grams of carbohydrates to support fueling of intense workouts and aid in the replenishment of glycogen stores - with No Added Sugar.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\">It enhanced with Creatine, Glutamine Peptides &amp; L-glutamine, Inositol, Choline, MCTs, and PABA.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\">Optimum Nutrition Serious Mass enriched with 25 Vitamins &amp; Essential Minerals with an emphasis on B-vitamins and Antioxidants.</li>\r\n</ul>', 2),
(48, 'QNT Massive Mass Gainer 2kg (Irish Chocolate)', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 15px; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0px !important;\">QNT MASSIVE MASS is a product designed for the ambitious athlete looking for a supplement that can support the development and maintenance of muscle mass and help in weight gain. The formula has been designed by the QNT Europe&rsquo;s Research Team to combine the most effective ingredients for optimal results in terms of weight and mass gain.All athletes and sports people who are serious about their goals, should include MASSIVE MASS in their daily diet to push their results to a new level. MASSIVE MASS mixes very easily in water or milk and, thanks to its delicious flavours, can be taken as a snack between meals, to provide the muscles with a balanced source of carbohydrates and protein.This formula is rich in WHEY PROTEIN and contains all essentials AMINO ACIDS as well as an excellent complex of vitamins and high-quality CARBOHYDRATES. MASSIVE MASS is suitable for individuals looking to gain weight as well as enhance their workout performance by providing nutrients such as carbohydrates, proteins, BCAAs, and added creatine and L-glutamine.</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"a-box-inner\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: Poppins; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: #474747; font-size: 1.5rem; background-color: #ffffff;\">Benefits</h2>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 15px; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none;\">Helps gain weight and muscle mass.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none;\">Provides carbohydrates as a major source of energy to fulfill your daily calorie needs to accomplish the weight gain goals.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none;\">Provides 25g of protein through whey protein concentrate(WPC) which helps in muscle growth and development along with 5.7g of BCAAs per serving which helps in post workout recovery.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none;\">Contains Creatine which helps to provide energy to muscles during intense workout improving performance.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: Poppins; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: #474747; font-size: 1.5rem; background-color: #ffffff;\">Ingredients</h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 15px; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0px !important;\">Diluents (Maltodextrin Powder, Sucrose, Dextrose), Whey Protein Concentrate, Cocoa Bean Extract, Creatine Monohydrate, Thickeners (INS 407 &amp; INS 466), Di-Calcium Phosphate, L-Glutamine, Magnesium Oxide, Ferric Pyrophosphate, Zinc Sulphate, Cupric Sulphate, Calcium D Pantothenate, Riboflavin 5&rsquo;&nbsp; Phosphate Sodium, Pyridoxine Hydrochloride, Potassium Iodide &amp; Cyanocobalamin.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 15px; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0px !important;\">Contains milk, soy, and gluten.&nbsp;This food supplement should not be used to replace a balanced and varied diet and a healthy way of life.&nbsp;Keep away from young children.&nbsp;Do not exceed the recommended dose.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: Poppins; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: #474747; font-size: 1.5rem; background-color: #ffffff;\">Usage</h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 15px; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0px !important;\">To prepare one serving, add a scoop of 150g (approx.) to a shaker and add 500 ml chilled water to it. Shake well and enjoy amazing WEIGHT GAINER.</p>', 'qnt-massive-mass-gaineR.webp', '<table class=\"table\" style=\"width: 1080px; max-width: 100%; margin-bottom: 1rem; background-color: #ffffff; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; font-size: 16px;\">\r\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<th style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: inherit; padding: 0.75rem; vertical-align: top; border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6; font-size: 15px;\">Brand</th>\r\n<td class=\"product_brand\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0.75rem; vertical-align: top; border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6; font-size: 14px;\">QNT</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<th style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: inherit; padding: 0.75rem; vertical-align: top; border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6; font-size: 15px;\">Flavour</th>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0.75rem; vertical-align: top; border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6; font-size: 14px;\">Irish Chocolate</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<th style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: inherit; padding: 0.75rem; vertical-align: top; border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6; font-size: 15px;\">Form</th>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0.75rem; vertical-align: top; border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6; font-size: 14px;\">Powder</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<th style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: inherit; padding: 0.75rem; vertical-align: top; border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6; font-size: 15px;\">Ideal For</th>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0.75rem; vertical-align: top; border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6; font-size: 14px;\">Man &amp; Woman</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<th style=\"box-sizing: b