(52, 'TM MASS GAINER (3KG)', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: #6b578b; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">What is a Mass Gainer?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: #6b578b; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">Mass gainers are high-calorie supplements that contain various levels of protein, fat, carbohydrates, minerals,&nbsp;vitamins, amino acids, and various other supplements. The amount of protein in a Mass Gainer may be less than that of&nbsp;Whey Protein&nbsp;but the level of carbohydrates and fats is certainly on a higher side. This high carb amount is necessary to boost the calorie intake.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: #6b578b; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: #6b578b; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Mass Gainer Benefits :</span></p>\r\n<ol style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Rich In Carbohydrates</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: #6b578b; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">Mass Gainers contain a rich amount of carbohydrates. These carbohydrates supply you with the required energy that is very helpful for an intense workout.</p>\r\n<ol style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\" start=\"2\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Contains&nbsp;High-Quality&nbsp;Whey Protei</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">n</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: #6b578b; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">Mass Gainers contain high quality of Whey Protein, which is an amazing supplement for bodybuilding. Some Mass Gainers also come with dietary fat. This dietary fat can help you achieve a lean physique.</p>\r\n<ol style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\" start=\"3\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Aids in Muscle Recovery &amp; Growth</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: #6b578b; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">Mass Gainers aid in muscle recovery and growth. This is very helpful when you are following a regular bodybuilding regime&nbsp;because you need to achieve desired results which&nbsp;requires&nbsp;good muscle recovery process to stay focused and regular with your workout.</p>\r\n<ol style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\" start=\"4\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Blend of Minerals &amp; Vitamins</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: #6b578b; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">Mass Gainers keep you healthy and fit. They are a good mix of different&nbsp;minerals and vitamins&nbsp;that are an important nourishment source for your body to stay healthy and fit.</p>\r\n<ol style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\" start=\"5\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Rich in Fiber</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: #6b578b; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">Mass Gainers contain fiber. This keeps you away from being bloated and improves digestion. It is a great way to achieve overall health and fitness.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: #6b578b; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: #6b578b; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Who should consume&nbsp;TM Mass Gainer?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: #6b578b; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">TM Mass Gainer is ideal for &ndash; weight lifters, people aiming for proper muscle gain, and those who want to gain weight in a healthy and balanced way.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: #6b578b; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: #6b578b; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">When to consume&nbsp;TM Mass Gainer?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: #6b578b; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">TM Mass Gainer provides the right balance of protein, carbohydrates, and other essential nutrients to help you put on weight in a healthy way. For best results have it as a post workout drink and have 1 &ndash; 2 servings per day or as suggested by your trainer.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: #6b578b; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: #6b578b; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">How to consume&nbsp;TM Mass Gainer?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: #6b578b; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">Mix a scoop of mass gainer with milk preferably or water. Shake well until the powder is completely dissolved and a smooth shake is formed and consume. Mixing with milk increases the amount of protein and calories of the shake.</p>', 'Team-Muscles--100%-Lean-Gainer.webp', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: #6b578b; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Per 150gm of&nbsp; TM Mass Gainer contains:</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #333333; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none;\">27g of Protein</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none;\">107.11g of Carbohydrates</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none;\">1.95g Dietary Fibers</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none;\">3.25g Fat</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none;\">0.95g Added Sugar</li>\r\n</ul>', 2),
