: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Helps Delay Fatigue During Prolonged Exercise So You Can Keep Intensity High For Longer.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; padding: 15px 0px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Supports Muscle Protein Synthesis, Which Helps The Body Increase The Level Of Muscle Protein Supporting Muscle</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; padding: 15px 0px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Helps Reduce The Level Of Muscle Soreness After Heavy Training</span></li>\r\n</ul>', 4),
