(55, 'Body Armour BCAA Ammunition', '<p>Body Armour BCAA Ammunition is a unique and innovative formula that has been made for you, to have just the right mix of essential amino acids to aid in protein synthesis, muscle recovery, repair damaged cells, build endurance and boost energy levels.</p>\r\n<p>Armoured with a superior formula having 7 g BCAA, 2.5 g of L-Glutamine infused with essential amino acids like Leucine, Isoleucine, Valine, L-Glutamine and vitamin B-6. Body Armour BCAA Ammunition provides the ammunition needed for the body to fuel a power-packed workout, each time.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Body Armour BCAA Ammunition gives you that extra energy to push your performance to the next level, helping your body recover from present workout and prepare for the next.</p>', 'Body-Armour-BCAA-Ammunition.webp', '<ul>\r\n<li>With 2:1:1 ratio BCAA delays fatigue during prolonged exercise</li>\r\n<li>Helps preserve muscle tissues during intense workout</li>\r\n<li>Helps activate protein synthesis while reducing catabolic muscle breakdown</li>\r\n<li>Helps in energy production</li>\r\n<li>BCAA fortifies immune system</li>\r\n</ul>', 4),
(56, ' BPI SPORT Best BCAA 30 Servings', '<div id=\"tab-1\" class=\"tab-content current\">\r\n<div class=\"part-content-txt\">\r\n<div id=\"descriptionAndDetails\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-extra-large\">\r\n<div id=\"productDescription_feature_div\" class=\"feature\">\r\n<div id=\"productDescription_feature_div\" class=\"a-row feature\">\r\n<div id=\"productDescription\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-small\">\r\n<p>BPI Sports&rsquo;&nbsp;<span class=\"bpiBlue\">BEST</span>&nbsp;BCAA&nbsp;is not your typical outdated, run-of-the-mill, same as everyone else, outdated BCAA product. Not even close.&nbsp;This formula is the first to bond the three branched chain amino acids &ndash; leucine, isoleucine and valine&nbsp;&ndash; utilizing a proprietary process route, to form oligopeptides (a bonded chain of amino acids; for example, a peptide linked chain). The oligopeptide-based branched chain amino acids may act as a better transport vehicle, allowing for more efficient metabolization, greater bio-activity, enhanced onset time, and a generally improved BCAA model. And, the scientific minds at BPI Sports didn&rsquo;t stop here.</p>\r\n<h2>Benefits</h2>\r\n<p>As discussed, taking branched chain amino acids in oligopeptide form, coupled in bio-active Oligopeptide-Enzymatic Technology, maybe the best way to overcome the typical metabolization and utilization limitations and realize the full promise &ndash; including:</p>\r\n<ul class=\"bold\">\r\n<li>SUPPORT MUSCLE PROTEIN SYNTHESIS.</li>\r\n<li>DECREASE PROTEIN CATABOLISM.</li>\r\n<li>SUPPORT ENDOGENOUS GLUCOSE PRODUCTION.</li>\r\n<li>ENHANCED RECOVERY FROM EXERCISE.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Ingredients</h2>\r\n<p>Oligopeptide-Enzymatic Technology&trade; (potassium hydroxide, stearic acid, carboxymethylcellulose sodium, crospovidone, natural waxes, carboxylic acids, Polyethylene Glycol, dicalcium phosphate), Maltodextrin, citric acid, natural and artificial flavors, malic acid, silica, fiber blend (cellulose gum, xanthan gum, carrageenan gum), sucralose, acesulfame-K, FD&amp;C Blue No. 1.</p>\r\n<h2>Usage</h2>\r\n<p>Take one (1) serving (1 scoop) blended into 8oz of ice cold water, either before, during, or after a workout, or as directed by a qualified healthcare practitioner. On non-training days, take one (1) serving (1 scoop) first thing in the morning, on an empty stomach, or as directed by a qualified healthcare practitioner.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'BPI--BEST-BCAA.webp', '<div class=\"key-features\">\r\n<p>Key Features:</p>\r\n<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-none\">\r\n<li>Best BCAA Shredded.</li>\r\n<li>Lean Muscle Recovery.</li>\r\n<li>Be Better. Be Stronger. BPI.</li>\r\n<li>Natural and Artificial Flavors.</li>\r\n<li>Lean Muscle Recovery Formula.</li>\r\n<li>Dietary Supplement.</li>\r\n<li>Promote lean muscle.</li>\r\n<li>Optimize recovery.</li>\r\n<li>Athletic performance.</li>\r\n<li>Support nitric oxide synthase.</li>\r\n<li>Burn fats for fuel.</li>\r\n<li>L-Citrulline oligopeptides.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 4),
(57, 'Gaspari Nutrition Amino Max 8000, 350 tablet(s), Unflavoured, 87 Servings', '', 'Gaspari-Nutrition-Amino-Max-8000-350-Tablets.webp', '<ul style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #212121; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\">\r\n<li style=\"color: #1a1a1a; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 20px; line-height: 20px; padding-right: 18px; position: relative; display: flex; align-items: center;\"><img style=\"color: #212121; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; width: 12px; margin-right: 5px; position: absolute; top: 10px; transform: translateY(-50%); left: 0px;\" src=\"https://static1.hkrtcdn.com/hknext/static/media/pdp/Component-icon-ic_Check.svg\" alt=\"\" />Comprise of&nbsp;BCAA</li>\r\n<li style=\"color: #1a1a1a; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 20px; line-height: 20px; padding-right: 18px; position: relative; display: flex; align-items: center;\"><img style=\"color: #212121; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; width: 12px; margin-right: 5px; position: absolute; top: 10px; transform: translateY(-50%); left: 0px;\" src=\"https://static1.hkrtcdn.com/hknext/static/media/pdp/Component-icon-ic_Check.svg\" alt=\"\" />Helps in&nbsp;Muscle Recovery</li>\r\n<li style=\"color: #1a1a1a; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 20px; line-height: 20px; padding-right: 18px; position: relative; display: flex; align-items: center;\"><img style=\"color: #212121; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; width: 12px; margin-right: 5px; position: absolute; top: 10px; transform: translateY(-50%); left: 0px;\" src=\"https://static1.hkrtcdn.com/hknext/static/media/pdp/Component-icon-ic_Check.svg\" alt=\"\" />Generally Consumed With Water</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 4),
(58, 'GAT BCAA POWDER', '', 'GAT-BCAA-POWDER.jpg', '<ul>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Delivers 5 grams BCAAs</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Instantized powder mixes easily</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">2:1:1 optimal ratio</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Unflavored powder is great for stacking</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\"&gt;</p>', 4),
(59, 'Kevin Levrone Gold BCAA 0.82 lbs, 375 g, 30 Servings', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 15px; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0px !important;\">GOLD BCAA 2:1:1.&nbsp;Food supplement. With sweeteners. A product that delivers branched-chain amino acids (BCAA) in 2:1:1 ratio, L-glutamine, citrulline malate, vitamins &amp; electrolytes. The product is intended for people with increased physical activity.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: Poppins; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: #474747; font-size: 1.5rem; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong>Benefits</strong></h2>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 15px; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none;\">The high concentration of leucine has a positive effect on the functioning of the nervous system and reduces fatigue by increasing the ratio of bcaa to tryptophan</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none;\">Facilitate quick muscle recovery after working out</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none;\">Help build and protect the muscles from diminishment during weight loss</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none;\">Ensures that your electrolytes are replaced as you sweat</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none;\">Helps you maintain your edge through even the most intense workouts</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: Poppins; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: #474747; font-size: 1.5rem; background-color: #ffffff;\">Ingredients</h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 15px; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0px !important;\">BCAA complex (L-leucine, L-isoleucine, L-valine), L-glutamine, citrulline malate, vitamins and minerals premix [potassium citrate, magnesium citrate, sodium citrate, vitamin C (L-ascorbic acid), vitamin B6 (pyridoxine hydrochloride), vitamin B12 (cyanocobalamin)], flavourings, anti-caking agents, acidity regulators (malic acid, citric acid), colours, sweeteners (steviol glycosides, sucralose, acesulfame K). The measure included in the packet serves to facilitate portioning, but it does not guarantee precise dosing. It is advisable to use scales in order to measure out the exact amount.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: Poppins; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: #474747; font-size: 1.5rem; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong>Usage</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 15px; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0px !important;\">Mix 1 scoop of powder (12,5 g) with 250 ml of water. Drink 1 portion immediately after a workout. Warnings: Do not use if you are allergic to any of the supplement compounds. Food supplements should not be used as a substitute for a varied and well-balanced diet. Do not exceed the recommended daily dose. Do not use if pregnant or nursing. Keep out of reach of young children. If you take medications, you should consult your doctor before you consume the product.</p>', 'KEVIN-LevroBCAA-4-1-1-RATIO.webp', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0px !important;\">Key Features:</p>\r\n<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-none\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Facilitate quick muscle recovery after working out</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Help build and protect the muscles from diminishment during weight loss</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Ensures that your electrolytes are replaced as you sweat</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Helps you maintain your edge through even the most intense workouts</span></li>\r\n</ul>', 4),
(60, 'Monster Series eXPAND Gold BCAAs', '', 'Monster-Series-eXPAND-Gold-BCAAs.webp', '', 4),
