474747; font-size: 1.5rem; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong>Usage</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 15px; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0px !important;\">Take one scoop (3 g) daily, mixed with water or juice.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 15px; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0px !important;\">On Training Days: Take immediately after workout.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 15px; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0px !important;\">On Non- Training Days: Take any time during the day. Do not exceed recommended dose. Drink plenty of water every day when supplementing creatine.</p>', 'Labrada-CreaLean-Powder.webp', '<div class=\"col-lg-5 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-12 mb-2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; width: 475px; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; -webkit-box-flex: 0; flex: 0 0 41.6667%; max-width: 41.6667%; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 0.5rem !important;\"><form style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" method=\"post\">\r\n<div class=\"product-details-content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div class=\"key-features\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 0px !important;\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></h1>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\">100% Pure Creatine Monohydrate</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\">Di