(75, 'Body Armour Glutamine Shield', '<p>Glutamine is the most common amino acid in our body. During intense training, Glutamine levels are greatly depleted in our body that decreases strength, stamina and recovery.</p>\r\n<p>Body Armour L-Glutamine Shield adds to the amino acids pool in the body and it prevents breaking down of body muscles. It helps in faster recovery from the intense workout.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Body Armour L-Glutamine Shield plays an important role in protein synthesis, intestinal health and serves as critical fuel source for our immune system.</p>', 'Body-Armour-Glutamine-Shield.webp', '<ul>\r\n<li>Boost protein synthesis in body</li>\r\n<li>Serves as fuel for immune system</li>\r\n<li>Most important nutrient for intestinal health</li>\r\n<li>Helps repair and build muscle</li>\r\n</ul>', 6);
