(76, 'Gaspari Nutrition Pure L-Glutamine Powder  Unflavoured I Post Workout Recovery, 0.55 lbs 250 gm (50 servings)', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 15px; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0px !important;\">Fly high and touch the sky of your fitness dreams with pure Glutamine by Gaspari Nutrition. It&rsquo;s the best way to maintain your fitness. It&rsquo;s carefully extracted to provide you the purest Glutamine extract possible so your workout regime doesn&rsquo;t slow down. This ideal post-workout supplement boosts muscle recovery, slows down muscle degeneration due to strenuous workouts and helps you gain muscle with Muscle protein synthesis (MPS) with ease.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: Poppins; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: #474747; font-size: 1.5rem; background-color: #ffffff;\">Benefits</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 15px; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Glutamine from Gaspari Nutrition has set a new standard for quality and purity amongst l-glutamine supplements</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">L-glutamine is a very slightly sweet, odourless, crystalline and pure powdered amino acid</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Pharmaceutical grade</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: Poppins; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: #474747; font-size: 1.5rem; background-color: #ffffff;\">Usage</h2>\r\n<div id=\"importantInformation_feature_div\" class=\"celwidget\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-feature-name=\"importantInformation\" data-cel-widget=\"importantInformation_feature_div\" data-csa-c-id=\"m4ngfl-d7jt5j-b2b4pd-cgzgs8\">\r\n<div id=\"important-information\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-extra-large bucket\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div class=\"a-section content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 15px;\">As a dietary food supplement, mix one serving of 5g (one level teaspoon) into at least 16 ounces (500 ml ) of water or other suitable liquid and drink within 15 minutes. Consume 1-2 servings per day. For best results, use this product as part of a proper diet and exercise program.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'GASPARI-PURE-GLUTAMINE-POWDER.webp', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0px !important;\">Key Features:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\">Ultimate workout supplement for high-strength training and long aerobic sessions</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\">Clean, pure and safe Glutamine to give you the best workout experience</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\