(100, 'EXERFIT PRE-WORKOUT', '<p><img src=\"https://www.exerfit.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Preworkout-R2-16-1-1.png\" /></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Poppins; line-height: 1.2; color: #444444; margin: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 30px; letter-spacing: 1px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Synergies that work</h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; font-family: Poppins; color: #3f3f3f; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Exerfit Preworkout includes ingredients that complement one another to prime the body for intense workouts, making it a complete pre-workout supplement. When it comes to supplement formulation, it is important to understand how synergies work. Certain ingredients work well when combined with other ingredients.</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; color: #3f3f3f; font-family: Poppins; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #444444; padding-top: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">No Proprietary blends</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />All Exerfit pre workout ingredients are clearly listed on the label with exact amounts. You deserve to know exactly what ingredients, and how much of each, are in the product you buy. Proprietary blends serve the purpose of hiding what&rsquo;s in the product. We think you deserve to know exactly what ingredients and how much of each are in the supplement.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Energy. Focus. Stamina.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Exerfit pre workout will help you stay energised, focused &amp; sustain for long with ingredients that promote ENERGY, FOCUS, and STAMINA and prove to be the best high-performance training fuel.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #444444; padding-top: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">Nutrients Vs stimu