thy Metabolic Rate</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none;\">Reduce body fat</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: Poppins; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: #474747; font-size: 1.5rem; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong>Ingredients</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 15px; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0px !important;\">Gelatin, Glycerol, Water.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: Poppins; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: #474747; font-size: 1.5rem; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong>Usage</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewDetail\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 15px;\">As a dietary supplement consume 1-2 CLA Core softgels with morning, noon, and evening meals or use as directed by a physician or licensed nutritionist.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'MusclePharm-CLA.webp', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 14px; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; letter-spacing: normal; margin-top: 0px !important;\">Key Features:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal;\">\r\n<li class=\"showHiddenFeatureBullets\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Naturally-occurring fatty acid found in meat, dairy, and safflower oil</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"showHiddenFeatureBullets\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">May help to reduce body fat and increase lean muscle</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"showHiddenFeatureBullets\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Highest quality, purity-and potency-conjugated linoleic acid (CLA) available</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"showHiddenFeatureBullets\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Builds super-lean mass while losing fat</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"showHiddenFeatureBullets\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Supports a healthy appetite level</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"showHiddenFeatureBullets\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Naturally-occurring fatty acid found in meat, dairy, and safflower oil May help to reduce body fat and increase lean muscle Highest quality, purity-and potency-conjugated linoleic acid (CLA) available Builds super-lean mass while losing fat Supports a healthy appetite level</span></li>\r\n</ul>', 10),
(118, 'MuscleTech-Healthcules-Hydroxycut', '', 'MuscleTech-Healthcules-Hydroxycut.webp', '<div class=\"excerpt ll-at-background\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: pill-gothic-600mg, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; overflow: visible; line-height: 21px;\">Hydroxycut Hardcore Elite provides a thermogenic and energy experience with unrivaled intensity, featuring a key weight loss ingredient.</div>\r\n<div class=\"product-bullets\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 25px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: pill-gothic-600mg, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\">\r\n<li class=\"ll-at-background\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: visible; line-height: 24px;\">INCREASE THERMOGENESIS**</li>\r\n<li class=\"ll-at-background\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: visible; line-height: 24px;\">SENSORY**</li>\r\n<li class=\"ll-at-background\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: visible; line-height: 24px;\">BOOST ENERGY &amp; FOCUS**</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 10),
(119, 'Muscletech Hydroxycut Hardcore NEXT GEN Ginger 100 Capsules', '<p>Benefits</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 15px; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0px !important;\">Every single capsule undergo a quality check with the benefits come intact and help in faster and effective weight loss. Consumption of the supplement delivers sensory experiences, which assures the awakened mind during a strenuous workout session. Subjects consuming the fat burner lost about 4 kilos in a matter of 60 days. You need to follow a strict diet and inculcate an exercise routine in your daily life.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: Poppins; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: #474747; font-size: 1.5rem; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Ingredients</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 15px; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0px !important;\">Green Coffee Bean Extract, Caffeine Anhydrous, Green Tea Extract, Red Sage extract, Blue Skullcap, Ginger, L-Ornithine HCI, Veggie Capsule, Magnesium Stearate, Silicon Dioxide, Standardized Salvianolic Acid</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: Poppins; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: #474747; font-size: 1.5rem; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Usage</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 15px; color: #212529; font-family: Poppins; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0px !important;\">Take each serving 30 to 60 minutes before the two largest meals of the day (eg. breakfast and lunch). Make sure you do not exceed 4 capsules in a 24-hour time frame. Avoid consuming within 5 hours of bedtime. For best results, use for 60 days in combination with diet and workout.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'MuscleTech-Performance-Series.webp', '<p>Muscletech Hydroxycut Hardcore Next Gen 100 is the world&rsquo;s first sustained-release next generation weight loss and extreme sensory formula that is scientifically tested for weight loss support.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\">It consists of a combination of Coleus, Forskolii, Yohimbe, Guayusa, and Blue Scullcap (Scutellaria) to deliver an unparalleled sensory effect.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\">Hydroxycut Hardcore Next Gen invokes thermogenesis in the body to speed up the metabolic rate. Thus, you are boosted for training harder and sculpt your body the way you want it to.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\">The key ingredients are mixed in a unique combination to deliver ultimate stimulation. It also contains Green Coffee for weight loss.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: disc; font-size: 14px;\">It is a complete package that is formulated uniquely to suffice your body needs and constantly remove unwanted fat in the process.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 10);
